{"tid":1409992,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［815大罷工］歡迎大家放低素材","createTime":"2019-08-05T00:22:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T04:34:50.000Z","uid":24938,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8ff7ace2430332d31566914b8632199558ca5423","tid":1409992,"uid":24938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T00:22:09.000Z","msg":"有一手或多手相可以擺低俾啲豬豬send 俾腦細睇<br />\n故事就由豬豬自己講俾腦細聽<br />\n<br />\n拋磚先 from tg group<br />\n屯門西鐵站有人打交<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CAiQ1uP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCAiQ1uP.png&h=1108eee5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nFrom 朋友一手 <br />\n天水圍西鐵塞死<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8cnBW3w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8cnBW3w.png&h=a633b643&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0e4be9978a41c6e8b1a9701cce0461b0ce7cb62b","tid":1409992,"uid":24938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T00:25:14.000Z","msg":"0819  from tg group<br />\n屯公深井塞到轉車站<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mEOBcC2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmEOBcC2.png&h=65523d12&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"05a9356c665e9d3d127ff6f5be94c4ffe7f73cd3","tid":1409992,"uid":248960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T00:30:39.000Z","msg":"此帖必火"},{"pid":"2354c8bb4b9f546d3f1c5eec61718162b0af7bed","tid":1409992,"uid":24938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T00:33:28.000Z","msg":"推啊"},{"pid":"5a94b37432c7a9b486ac5d300e17909ac56a632a","tid":1409992,"uid":24938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T00:33:47.000Z","msg":"【0825】港鐵宣佈觀塘線、荃灣線及東鐵線服務暫停，現時共有六條線服務受阻。<br />\n<br />\n港島線：銅鑼灣站往返鰂魚涌站服務暫停<br />\n荃灣線：尖沙咀站往返葵興站服務暫停<br />\n觀塘線：九龍塘站往返觀塘站<br />\n東涌線：南昌站往返青衣站服務暫停<br />\n西鐵線：錦上路站往返屯門站服務暫停<br />\n東鐵綫：九龍塘站往返羅湖站及落馬洲站服務暫停<br />\n<br />\n另外，屯門站因有衝突情況，車站需要關閉。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cMeHSFT.png\" data-thu